INSERT INTO `comments` VALUES
(4,33,'code-review-bot','## Code Review Passed (2026-07-12)\n\n**Test**: CRUD Smoke Test (60/60 passed)\n\n**验证范围**:\n- Project CRUD: create/read/update/delete\n- Epic CRUD: create/read/update/delete\n- Story CRUD: create/read/update/delete\n- Task CRUD: create/read/update/delete + status transitions\n- Task spec/append\n- Comments CRUD\n- Search (status/priority/q filters)\n- Sprint CRUD + activate/complete\n- Error handling (404/422)\n- Meta endpoint (types/statuses/priorities/sprint_statuses)\n\n**注意**: Docker 容器代码已通过 docker cp 更新到最新版本（含 Sprint 端点）。','2026-07-12 05:19:26','2026-07-12 05:19:26'),
(5,34,'code-review-bot','## Code Review Passed (2026-07-12)\n\n**Test**: MCP service layer shared verification\n\n**验证范围**:\n- MCP 服务器使用 AGENTBOARD_MCP_BACKEND=db 模式，直接 from . import service 导入同一 service 层\n- MCP get_task(33) 返回数据与 REST API GET /api/tasks/33 完全一致\n- MCP 工具列表完整 (30 tools)\n- MCP HTTP 端点 (8001/mcp) 响应正常\n- Sprint service 函数在 MCP 容器中可用\n\n**结论**: MCP 与 REST API 确实共用同一 service.py 层。','2026-07-12 05:19:26','2026-07-12 05:19:26'),
(6,82,'Code Review Automation','## Code Review 结果：通过 ✅\n\n**审查时间**: 2026-07-12 14:10\n\n### 测试结果\n- **Sprint API 冒烟测试**: 46/46 通过\n\n### 测试覆盖范围\n1. **认证**: Login + Token 获取 ✓\n2. **Meta API**: `/api/meta` 包含 `sprint_statuses: [planning, active, completed]` ✓\n3. **Sprint CRUD**: Create (默认 planning 状态) / List / Get / Update (PATCH) / Delete ✓\n4. **Sprint 激活**: `POST /sprints/{sid}/activate` → 状态变更为 active ✓\n5. **单 active Sprint 约束**: 激活第二个 Sprint 时自动停用第一个 ✓\n6. **Task-Sprint 分配**: TaskIn 创建时不带 sprint_id，通过 `PATCH /tasks/{tid}` 设置 `sprint_id` ✓\n7. **Sprint 任务列表**: `GET /sprints/{sid}/tasks` 返回正确数量 ✓\n8. **Sprint 完成 + 任务退回**: `POST /sprints/{sid}/complete` → Sprint 变 completed，未完成任务退回 backlog，sprint_id 清空 ✓\n\n### 发现并修复的基础设施问题（非 Sprint 功能 bug）\n1. **CORS 401 响应缺失头**: `require_business_auth` 中间件返回 401 时未带 CORS 头，导致浏览器无法读取错误响应。已修复：手动在 401 JSONResponse 中添加 `Access-Control-Allow-Origin` 和 `Access-Control-Allow-Credentials`。\n\n### 结论\nSprint 数据模型、REST API、状态机、单 active Sprint 约束、任务退回逻辑全部正常工作。状态更新为 **done**。','2026-07-12 06:10:49','2026-07-12 06:10:49'),
(7,83,'Code Review Automation','## Code Review 结果：通过 ✅\n\n**审查时间**: 2026-07-12 14:10\n\n### 测试结果\n- **Sprint UI E2E 测试 (Playwright)**: 13/13 通过\n\n### 测试覆盖范围\n1. **SPA 加载**: 页面正常渲染，标题为 AgentBoard ✓\n2. **登录 UI**: 点击\"登录\"按钮 → 填写用户名/密码 → 提交登录 ✓\n3. **项目导航**: 登录后项目列表正确显示，可点击进入项目 ✓\n4. **Sprint 视图导航**: Sprint 导航链接可点击，Sprint UI 正确渲染 ✓\n5. **Sprint 创建 UI**: 点击\"创建\" → 模态框打开 → 填写标题 → 点击\"创建\"按钮 → Sprint 出现在列表 ✓\n6. **Sprint 激活 UI**: 点击\"启动\"按钮 → Sprint 状态变为 active ✓\n7. **Sprint 完成 UI**: 点击\"完成\"按钮 → Sprint 状态变为 completed ✓\n8. **控制台无异常错误**: 无 JS 错误、无未预期 401 ✓\n\n### 发现并修复的基础设施问题（非 Sprint UI bug）\n1. **Web 容器 `web_app.py` 过期**: 容器中缺少 catch-all 路由 `@app.get(\"/{path:path}\")`，导致 Angular 构建产物（`main-*.js`, `styles-*.css`）返回 404。已通过 `docker cp` 注入最新代码修复。\n2. **CORS 401 响应缺失头**: 同 Task #82，已修复。\n\n### 结论\nAngular 前端 Sprint 管理 UI（列表/创建/启动/完成 + 任务分配）全部正常工作。状态更新为 **done**。','2026-07-12 06:10:49','2026-07-12 06:10:49'),
(8,84,'Senior Developer (Agent)','## 完成记录\n\n**日期**: 2026-07-12\n**状态**: in_review\n\n### MCP Sprint 工具（8 个新增）\n- `list_sprints` / `get_sprint` / `create_sprint` / `update_sprint` / `activate_sprint` / `complete_sprint` / `delete_sprint` / `list_sprint_tasks`\n- 支持 db/api 双后端，与现有工具模式一致\n\n### Backlog Web 视图\n- Angular 前端项目视图新增 Backlog 区域\n- 展示未分配 Sprint 的任务列表，含状态/优先级徽章 + 搜索过滤\n- `backlogTasks` signal + `loadBacklog()` + `backlogVisibleTasks` computed\n\n### 验证\n- 回归测试: backend_flow 3/3 + web_flow 3/3 + playwright_e2e 6/6 = 12 passed\n- MCP Sprint 工具端到端验证通过\n\n**Story**: Story 12.2 (in_progress)\n**Epic**: Epic 12','2026-07-12 07:35:28','2026-07-12 07:35:28'),
(9,85,'Senior Developer (Agent)','## 完成记录\n\n**日期**: 2026-07-12\n**状态**: in_review\n\n### 附件数据模型与存储\n- models.py: 新增 Attachment 模型 (id/task_id/filename/original_name/size/mime_type/created_at)\n- service.py: create_attachment/get_attachment/list_attachments/delete_attachment + 文件磁盘存储\n- api.py: POST upload / GET download / GET info / DELETE 端点\n- Alembic 迁移 9e4f1d5c8a3b_add_attachments.py\n- 安全: 10MB 限制、MIME 白名单、CASCADE 删除、UUID 文件名\n\n验证: curl 全链路通过; 回归 12/12 passed\n\nStory: Story 12.3 (in_progress)\nEpic: Epic 12','2026-07-12 07:41:57','2026-07-12 07:41:57'),
(10,85,'code-review-bot','## Code Review Result: PASS ✅\n\n**Review Date**: 2026-07-12 15:50\n**Tests**: 16/16 passed\n\n### Attachment API Tests\n- ✅ Upload valid attachment (text/plain) - metadata correct (id, task_id, original_name, size, mime_type, filename)\n- ✅ List attachments by task\n- ✅ Get attachment info\n- ✅ Download attachment (content matches original)\n- ✅ Upload PNG image (MIME whitelist)\n- ✅ Upload PDF (MIME whitelist)\n- ✅ Reject invalid MIME type (exe -> 422)\n- ✅ Reject oversized file (>10MB -> 422)\n- ✅ Upload to non-existent task (404)\n- ✅ Get non-existent attachment info (404)\n- ✅ Delete attachment\n- ✅ Deleted attachment returns 404 (DB record removed)\n- ✅ Delete non-existent attachment (404)\n- ✅ UUID filename security (32-char hex, no path traversal vectors)\n- ✅ List attachments on non-existent task (404)\n- ✅ Attachment model fields verified: id, task_id, filename (UUID), original_name, size, mime_type, created_at\n\n### Security Verification\n- **UUID filename**: Stored as 32-char hex UUID, not original filename - prevents path traversal\n- **MIME whitelist**: 11 types allowed (png, jpeg, gif, webp, svg, pdf, txt, markdown, csv, json, xml, zip, gzip)\n- **Size limit**: 10MB enforced via `ATTACHMENT_MAX_SIZE` env var\n- **CASCADE delete**: Attachment records cleaned up when parent task deleted\n\n### Test Script\n- `tests/test_review_84_85.py` (35 tests total, covering both Task #84 and #85)','2026-07-12 07:54:04','2026-07-12 07:54:04'),
(11,84,'code-review-bot','## Code Review Result: PASS ✅\n\n**Review Date**: 2026-07-12 15:50\n**Tests**: 19/19 passed\n\n### Sprint API Tests (12/12 passed)\n- ✅ Create sprint (POST /api/projects/{pid}/sprints)\n- ✅ Get sprint by id\n- ✅ List sprints by project\n- ✅ Activate sprint\n- ✅ Create task in sprint (POST /api/stories/{sid}/tasks + PATCH sprint_id)\n- ✅ Create backlog task (no sprint_id)\n- ✅ List sprint tasks\n- ✅ Update sprint (PATCH goal)\n- ✅ Complete sprint (status -> completed)\n- ✅ Task backfill after sprint completion (sprint_id -> null)\n- ✅ Delete sprint\n- ✅ Single active sprint constraint: enforced via auto-deactivation (activating S2 auto-sets S1 back to planning, maintaining exactly 1 active sprint)\n\n### Backlog Web View (2/2 passed)\n- ✅ Web SPA loads correctly\n- ✅ Backlog section found in Angular JS bundle\n\n### MCP Sprint Tools (2/2 passed)\n- ✅ MCP initialize successful\n- ✅ 8 Sprint MCP tools confirmed: list_sprints, get_sprint, create_sprint, update_sprint, activate_sprint, complete_sprint, delete_sprint, list_sprint_tasks\n\n### Notes\n- Single active sprint constraint uses auto-deactivate approach (not reject) - valid design choice\n- All Sprint CRUD + lifecycle operations working correctly\n- MCP tools accessible via HTTP Streamable HTTP transport\n\n### Test Script\n- `tests/test_review_84_85.py` (35 tests total, covering both Task #84 and #85)','2026-07-12 07:54:04','2026-07-12 07:54:04'),
(12,88,'Code Review Bot','## 代码审查结果：测试失败\n\n### 测试执行\n- **通过**: 7/11\n- **失败**: 4/11\n\n### 通过的测试\n- ✅ `test_compute_next_run_hourly_boundary` - 小时边界 cron 计算\n- ✅ `test_compute_next_run_every_minute` - 每分钟 cron 计算\n- ✅ `test_compute_next_run_invalid_returns_none` - 非法表达式返回 None\n- ✅ `test_compute_next_run_for_once_future` - 未来一次性调度\n- ✅ `test_compute_next_run_for_once_past` - 过期一次性调度\n- ✅ `test_scan_disabled_schedule_not_triggered` - disabled 不触发\n- ✅ `test_scan_future_schedule_not_triggered` - 未来时间不触发\n\n### 失败的测试（全部 4 个都因同一根因）\n- ❌ `test_scan_triggers_due_cron_schedule`\n- ❌ `test_scan_idempotent_no_duplicate_run`\n- ❌ `test_scan_once_schedule_disables_after_run`\n- ❌ `test_daemon_scheduler_single_scan`\n\n### 根因分析\n\n`scheduler.py` 的 `_trigger_one()` 函数使用 `SELECT ... FOR UPDATE NOWAIT`（L138-144）实现行级锁。这个语法 **SQLite 不支持**，导致所有实际触发逻辑被静默跳过：\n\n```python\ntry:\n    locked = s.execute(\n        text(\"SELECT 1 FROM agent_schedules WHERE id = :sid FOR UPDATE NOWAIT\"),\n        {\"sid\": schedule.id},\n    ).fetchone()\nexcept Exception:\n    # 被其他实例持有锁，跳过\n    log.debug(\"schedule %d locked by another instance, skip\", schedule.id)\n    return False  # ← SQLite 永远走这里\n```\n\n### 修复建议\n\n方案 A（推荐）：根据数据库后端选择锁策略\n- `sqlite`: 跳过行锁（SQLite 本身是单写者，WAL 模式下读不阻塞写），直接进入幂等检查\n- `mysql/mariadb`: 使用 `FOR UPDATE NOWAIT`\n\n方案 B：使用文件锁或应用层乐观锁替代数据库行锁\n\n方案 C：测试中 mock 行锁，但会降低测试价值\n\n### 注意\n- MariaDB/MySQL 8.0+ 支持 `FOR UPDATE NOWAIT`，生产环境不受影响\n- 幂等键检查、cron 计算器、once 调度逻辑本身是正确的','2026-07-12 12:40:05','2026-07-12 12:40:05'),
(16,89,'Code Review Automation','## Code Review 通过 ✅ (2026-07-12 22:39)\n\n**测试结果**: 11/11 passed (7.47s)\n\n| 测试用例 | 结果 |\n|---------|------|\n| `test_compute_next_run_hourly_boundary` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_compute_next_run_every_minute` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_compute_next_run_invalid_returns_none` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_compute_next_run_for_once_future` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_compute_next_run_for_once_past` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_scan_triggers_due_cron_schedule` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_scan_idempotent_no_duplicate_run` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_scan_disabled_schedule_not_triggered` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_scan_future_schedule_not_triggered` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_scan_once_schedule_disables_after_run` | ✅ PASSED |\n| `test_daemon_scheduler_single_scan` | ✅ PASSED |\n\n### 验证要点\n- **幂等键机制**: `schedule:{id}:{YYYYMMDDHHmmss}` 格式，二次触发正确跳过（test_scan_idempotent_no_duplicate_run）\n- **多实例 Lease**: MySQL/MariaDB 环境使用 `SELECT FOR UPDATE NOWAIT`；SQLite 降级为幂等键兜底\n- **状态推进**: once 类型触发后 `next_run_at` 置 None；cron 类型正确推进到下次\n- **边界处理**: 禁用/未来 schedule 不触发；非法 cron 表达式返回 None\n- **守护进程**: DaemonScheduler 线程正常启停和扫描\n\n结论：**调度扫描器的租约与幂等键机制实现正确，所有核心路径测试通过。**','2026-07-12 14:39:25','2026-07-12 14:39:25'),
